- Hi.

125
00:07:47,567 --> 00:07:49,694
I'm here for the interview
at <i>Alette</i> magazine.

126
00:07:49,735 --> 00:07:53,967
<i>Alette...</i> Oh, filled, internally.
Yesterday.

127
00:07:54,006 --> 00:07:56,770
