128
00:07:56,809 --> 00:08:01,803
Oh...
Speak of the devil.

129
00:08:01,848 --> 00:08:03,975
<i>[#</i> The Pussycat Dolls: <i>Bad Girl]</i>

130
00:08:04,016 --> 00:08:07,611
Alicia... Billington.

131
00:08:20,199 --> 00:08:22,895
She has the longest legs in the world.

132
00:08:22,935 --> 00:08:25,028
