133
00:08:26,606 --> 00:08:29,803
Great. [sighs] Faulty.

134
00:08:29,842 --> 00:08:33,744
- Nice scarf.
- Thanks. I bought it for the interview.

135
00:08:35,648 --> 00:08:38,116
<i>Scusi...</i>
[whispering] Come on.

136
00:08:40,953 --> 00:08:44,548
As we speak, interviews are being held

